synopsis: Picking up where The Suicide Squad (2021) left off, Peacemaker returns home after recovering from his encounter with Bloodsport - only to discover that his freedom comes at a price.
In a desperate attempt to pay off a mounting bar tab, a band of misfits end up on a quest to save the realm of Exandria from dark, magical forces.
A blind lawyer by day, vigilante by night. Matt Murdock fights the crime of New York as Daredevil.
A group of vigilantes set out to take down corrupt superheroes who abuse their superpowers.
A widowed single mom discovers that her son has super powers and tries to figure out how to raise him safely and responsibly.
A team of young superheroes combat evil and other perils.
Jedi Knights lead the Grand Army of the Republic against the droid army of the Separatists.
After the murder of his family, Marine veteran Frank Castle becomes the vigilante known as "The Punisher," with only one goal in mind: to avenge them.
After being struck by lightning, Barry Allen wakes up from his coma to discover he's been given the power of super speed, becoming the Flash, fighting crime in Central City.
The world's most famous superhero and comic books' most famous journalist face the pressures and complexities that come with balancing work, justice and parenthood in today's society.
A family of former child heroes, now grown apart, must reunite to continue to protect the world.
The mercurial villain Loki resumes his role as the God of Mischief in a new series that takes place after the events of “Avengers: Endgame.”
The missions of the Strategic Homeland Intervention, Enforcement and Logistics Division.
Exploring pivotal moments from the Marvel Cinematic Universe and turning them on their head, leading the audience into uncharted territory.
The story behind Detective James Gordon's rise to prominence in Gotham City in the years before Batman's arrival.

Spoiled billionaire playboy Oliver Queen is missing and presumed dead when his yacht is lost at sea. He returns five years later a changed man, determined to clean up the city as a hooded vigilante armed with a bow.
An adult animated series based on the Skybound/Image comic about a teenager whose father is the most powerful superhero on the planet.

Following the tragic end of her brief superhero career, Jessica Jones tries to rebuild her life as a private investigator, dealing with cases involving people with remarkable abilities in New York City.
Time-travelling rogue Rip Hunter has to recruit a rag-tag team of heroes and villains to help prevent an apocalypse that could impact not only Earth, but all of time.
The adventures of an idealistic mad scientist and his field team of superpowered outcasts.
A brave and clever ragtag starship crew stands up against the evil Empire as it tightens its grip on the galaxy and hunts down the last of the Jedi Knights.
In a war-torn world of elemental magic, a young boy reawakens to undertake a dangerous mystic quest to fulfill his destiny as the Avatar, and bring peace to the world.

show_title: Miraculous: Tales of Ladybug & Cat Noir
synopsis: Marinette and Adrien, two normal teens, transform into superheroes Ladybug and Cat Noir when an evil threatens their city.
A superhero-loving boy without any powers is determined to enroll in a prestigious hero academy and learn what it really means to be a hero.
The 'Bad Batch' of elite and experimental clones make their way through an ever-changing galaxy in the immediate aftermath of the Clone Wars.
The adventures of Superman's cousin in her own superhero career.
Batwoman seeks justice for Gotham City.
A warrior chosen as the latest and last Wu Assassin must search for the powers of an ancient triad and restore balance in San Francisco's Chinatown.

Naruto Uzumaki, is a loud, hyperactive, adolescent ninja who constantly searches for approval and recognition, as well as to become Hokage, who is acknowledged as the leader and strongest of all ninja in the village.

When a sabotaged experiment gives him super strength and unbreakable skin, Luke Cage becomes a fugitive attempting to rebuild his life in Harlem and must soon confront his past and fight a battle for the heart of his city.
A young man is bestowed with incredible martial arts skills and a mystical force known as the Iron Fist.
The story of the Joestar family, who are possessed with intense psychic strength, and the adventures each member encounters throughout their lives.
Naruto Uzumaki, a mischievous adolescent ninja, struggles as he searches for recognition and dreams of becoming the Hokage, the village's leader and strongest ninja.
Two brothers search for a Philosopher's Stone after an attempt to revive their deceased mother goes awry and leaves them in damaged physical forms.
Common people discover that they have super powers. Their lives intertwine as a devastating event must be prevented.
Teenager Courtney Whitmore joins the Justice Society of America. Based on the character from DC Comics.
The story of Saitama, a hero that does it just for fun & can defeat his enemies with a single punch.
David Haller is a troubled young man diagnosed as schizophrenic, but after a strange encounter, he discovers special powers that will change his life forever.
High school student Ichigo Kurosaki, who has the ability to see ghosts, gains soul reaper powers from Rukia Kuchiki and sets out to save the world from "Hollows".
Teenage superheroes strive to prove themselves as members of the Justice League.
The series focuses on a single Harley Quinn, who sets off to make it on her own in Gotham City.
It tells the tale of a wronged Japanese snow monkey, mentored by the ghost of an American assassin, as he cuts a wide swath through the Tokyo underworld.
A group of teenagers steal a derelict Starfleet vessel and use it to explore the galaxy.
A group of young offenders doing community service get struck by lightning during a storm, and begin to develop superpowers.
Avatar Korra fights to keep Republic City safe from the evil forces of both the physical and spiritual worlds.

In 1946, Peggy Carter is relegated to secretarial duties in the Strategic Scientific Reserve (SSR). When Howard Stark is accused of treason, he secretly recruits Peggy to clear his name with the help of his butler, Edwin Jarvis.
The Dark Knight battles crime in Gotham City with occasional help from Robin and Batgirl.
Teenage superheroes strive to prove themselves as members of the Justice League.
The futuristic misadventures and tragedies of an easygoing bounty hunter and his partners.
The series focuses on a single Harley Quinn, who sets off to make it on her own in Gotham City.
It tells the tale of a wronged Japanese snow monkey, mentored by the ghost of an American assassin, as he cuts a wide swath through the Tokyo underworld.
A lone crimefighter battles the forces of evil with the help of a virtually indestructible and artificially intelligent supercar.
The Caped Crusader and his young ward battle evildoers in Gotham City.
The adventures of a secret Agent armed with almost infinite scientific resourcefulness.
A group of teenagers steal a derelict Starfleet vessel and use it to explore the galaxy.
When a sixteen-year-old high school student finds out she's a witch, her two aunts offer guidance on how to control her newly-discovered magical powers.
With the help of the powerful Dragonballs, a team of fighters led by the saiyan warrior Goku defend the planet earth from extraterrestrial enemies.
Four Vietnam vets, framed for a crime they didn't commit, help the innocent while on the run from the military.
A group of young offenders doing community service get struck by lightning during a storm, and begin to develop superpowers.
Avatar Korra fights to keep Republic City safe from the evil forces of both the physical and spiritual worlds.

In 1946, Peggy Carter is relegated to secretarial duties in the Strategic Scientific Reserve (SSR). When Howard Stark is accused of treason, he secretly recruits Peggy to clear his name with the help of his butler, Edwin Jarvis.
Vanessa Helsing, distant relative of famous vampire hunter Abraham Van Helsing, is resurrected only to find that vampires have taken over the world.
Star Wars anthology series that will see some of the world's best anime creators bring their talent to this beloved universe.
The support crew serving on one of Starfleet's least important ships, the U.S.S. Cerritos, have to keep up with their duties, often while the ship is being rocked by a multitude of sci-fi anomalies.
Looking for a part-time job, 13-year-old Henry Hart finds himself helping super hero Captain Man as his sidekick, keeping the secret from his family and friends.
The adventures and romance of a sensitive and cultured lion-man and a crusading assistant district attorney in Manhattan, New York City.

A wealthy mystery man named Charlie runs a detective agency via a speakerphone and his personal assistant, John Bosley. His detectives are three beautiful women, who end up in a variety of difficult situations.

The first generation of superheroes has kept the world safe for nearly a century. Now their children must live up to their legacy in an epic drama that spans decades and navigates the dynamics of family, power and loyalty.
An isolated community of superhumans fight to protect themselves.
A 20th-century astronaut emerges out of 500 years of suspended animation into a future time to become Earth's greatest hero.

Led by a boy named Ryder, a team of six playful rescue dogs use their individual talents to protect the seaside town of Adventure Bay. The pups are occasionally joined by newer helpers: Cap'n Turbot, Robo-Dog, Everest, and Tracker.
These siblings with superpowers might be twins, but they are very different indeed.
In a world where mutated humans are treated with distrust and fear, an institute for mutants battles to achieve peaceful co-existence with humanity.

A team of intergalactic warriors fights to protect the universe, but the combination of three highly trained beings and one quirky young boy leaves the team struggling to overcome the dangerous scenarios that are put in front of them.
Phineas and Ferb invent, scheme, and stay one step ahead of their bratty sister. Meanwhile, their pet platypus plots against evil Dr. Doofenshmirtz.
As part of a deal with an intelligence agency to look for his missing brother, a renegade pilot goes on missions with an advanced battle helicopter.

After discovering their parents are super-villains in disguise, a group of teenagers band together to run away from their homes in order to atone for their parents' actions and to discover the secrets of their origins.
The war for Eternia begins again in what may be the final battle between He-Man and Skeletor. A new animated series from writer-director Kevin Smith.
A crusading school principal gets back into action as the original African-American electrical superhero.

show_title: Lois & Clark: The New Adventures of Superman
synopsis: In addition to fighting evil, Superman has a burning romance with Lois Lane in both of his identities.
The story of Ben Tennyson, a typical kid who becomes very atypical after he discovers the Omnitrix, a mysterious alien device with the power to transform the wearer into ten different alien species.
A team of teenagers with attitude are recruited to save Angel Grove from the evil witch, Rita Repulsa, and later, Lord Zedd, Emperor of all he sees, and their horde of monsters.
A team of mutant superheroes fight for justice and human acceptance in the Marvel Comics universe.
A young man with spider-like abilities fights crime as a superhero in New York City while trying to have a normal personal life.
Abby Arcane returns home to Marais, Louisiana to investigate a deadly swamp-borne virus, only to discover the dark, terrifying mysteries of the swamp.
Six months after the defeat of Majin Buu, The mighty Saiyan Son Goku continues his quest on becoming stronger.
The adventures of the greatest of the female superheroes.
Pop culture references fly thick and fast as stop-motion animation is featured in sketches lampooning everything from television movies to comic books.
A psychic middle school boy tries to live a normal life and keep his growing powers under control, even though he constantly gets into trouble.
A fugitive scientist has the curse of becoming a powerful green monster under extreme emotional stress.

Assembled is a comprehensive documentary series that chronicles the creation of Marvel Studios' thrilling new shows and theatrical releases. Assembled is an immersive, and in-depth examination of the next phase of the MCU.
A group of genetically-enhanced children escape from a lab project. Years later we meet Max, one of the escapees who now works for a messenger service in the post-apocalyptic Pacific Northwest.
A quirky spy show of the adventures of eccentrically suave British Agent John Steed and his predominately female partners.
Son Gokû, a fighter with a monkey tail, goes on a quest with an assortment of odd characters in search of the Dragon Balls, a set of crystals that can give its bearer anything they desire.
A heroic drama that follows capable but bad cop Ryoo Soo-yeol regaining his humanity after meeting the righteous but crazy 'K'.
A samurai, sent through time, fights to return home and save the world.
The events and battles of the Galactic Republic's last major war are recounted.
Simon "The Saint" Templar, a wealthy adventurer and 20th Century Robin Hood, travels the world in his white Volvo P1800S to solve the unsolvable and right wrongs.
A team of five teenaged superheroes save the world from many villains around their city while experiencing things normal teens face today.
Discovering his ties to a secret ancient order, a young man living in modern Istanbul embarks on a quest to save the city from an immortal enemy.

show_title: She-Ra and the Princesses of Power
synopsis: She-Ra, Princess of Power, leads a rebellion to free her land of Etheria from the monstrous invaders the Horde.

In a world where superheroes have been real for decades, an accountant with no superpowers comes to realize his city is owned by a super villain. As he struggles to uncover this conspiracy, he falls in league with a strange blue superhero.
Superhero roommates Robin, Cyborg, Starfire, Raven and Beast Boy love saving the day, but what happens when they're done fighting crime?

When an army of powerful alien beings is unleashed on Earth threatening life as we know it, a brand-new team of Power Rangers, fueled by the prehistoric power of the dinosaurs, are recruited to deal with the threat.
After a severely injured test pilot is rebuilt with nuclear-powered bionic limbs and implants, he serves as an intelligence agent.
A retired Intelligence Agent turned private detective helps various threatened clients to equalize the odds.
Four ninja turtles, mutated by a mysterious alien substance, must rise up out of the sewers and defend their city against evil forces from both the past and present.
Seven of the most formidable heroes form arguably the most powerful team ever.
Maxwell Smart, a highly intellectual but bumbling spy working for the CONTROL agency, battles the evil forces of rival spy agency KAOS with the help of his competent partner Agent 99.
A teacher is asked to be a superhero using a special alien suit with powers he can barely understand or control.

In this Nick Jr. television show, a pink-haired girl named Stephanie moves to LazyTown with her uncle (the mayor of LazyTown), where she tries to teach its extremely lazy residents that physical activity is beneficial.
The further adventures of the Marvel Universe's mightiest general membership superhero team.
After being tortured and humiliated by his babysitter, a ten year old boy is put under the care of two fairy godparents, who can grant him almost any wish, which leads to dire consequences.
A handsome secret agent and his team of LGBTQ superspies embark on extraordinary adventures.
When a failed alchemical ritual leaves brothers Edward and Alphonse Elric with severely damaged bodies, they begin searching for the one thing that can save them; the fabled philosopher's stone.
A police forensic scientist, Barry Allen, battles crimes as the super-fast superhero "The Flash".
The adventures of a quartet of humanoid warrior turtles and their friends.
Fuelled by remorse and vengeance, a high schooler named Terry McGinnis revives the role of Batman. Under supervision of an elderly Bruce Wayne, he fights crime in a harsh, futuristic Gotham.
A continuation of the Justice League animated series finds the original members of the team joined in their battle against crime and evil by dozens of other heroes from the DC comics universe.
A man struggling with his faith who is haunted by the sins of his past is suddenly thrust into the role of defending humanity from the gathering forces of darkness.
A probationary angel, sent back to Earth, teams with an ex-cop to help people.
The adventures of a Shaolin Monk as he wanders the American West armed only with his skill in Kung Fu.
Two teenagers from very different backgrounds find themselves burdened and awakened to newly acquired superpowers while growing closer together every day.
Fifteen-year-old Ben Tennyson must utilize the Omnitrix yet again in order to locate his missing Grandpa Max, accompanied by his cousin Gwen and former enemy Kevin 11.
The Man of Steel fights crime with help from his friends at the Daily Planet.
The bizarre escapades of pseudo-heroic scientist Dr. Rusty Venture, his competent, high-strung bodyguard, and his two overenthusiastic sons.
A group of teenage friends and their Great Dane (Scooby-Doo) travel in a bright green van solving strange and hilarious mysteries, while returning from or going to a regular teenage function.
When darkness get strengthened to destroy the world, Suryanshis chose Shaktimaan in order to fight against the forces of evil.
Spider-Man battles evil with a new team of teen colleagues and training from S.H.I.E.L.D.
An ordinary boy finds a magic amulet that chooses him to be a Trollhunter, a guardian that defends the world of humans and the secret world of trolls.
The continuing adventures of Ben Tennyson (Yuri Lowenthal) and his new partner, Rook Blonko (Bumper Robinson).
The untold story of Superman's grandfather as he fights for justice on his home planet.

show_title: Star vs. the Forces of Evil
synopsis: Star Butterfly arrives on Earth to live with the Diazes, a Mexican-American family. She continues to battle villains throughout the universe and high school, mainly to protect her extremely powerful wand, an object that still confuses her.
With his secret identity now revealed to the world, Ben Tennyson continues to fight evil as a superhero with the help of the newly acquired Ultimatrix.
Billionaire Bruce Wayne fights crime and evil as the mysterious Batman.
A high school cheerleader and her accident-prone best friend balance their duties as global crime-fighters with the typical challenges of adolescence.
Follow Peter Parker, Gwen Stacy, and Miles Morales and their adventures as the young heroes team up with Hulk, Ms. Marvel, and Black Panther to take down foes like Rhino, Doc Oock, and Green Goblin.
Scooby-Doo and the gang attempt to solve creepy mysteries in the town of Crystal Cove, a place with a history of eerie supernatural events.
The continuing adventures of the staff of the ghost removal service.
A clan of heroic night creatures pledge to protect modern New York City as they did in Scotland one thousand years earlier.
The misadventures of a milkshake, an order of fries, a meatball, and their retired next door neighbor in the suburbs of New Jersey.
When the fate of their world, Ninjago, is challenged by great threats, it's up to the ninja: Kai, Jay, Cole, Zane, Lloyd and Nya to save the world.
The continuing adventures of a quartet of turtle superheroes.
An animated television show that focuses on a sixteen-year-old Peter Parker, and the origins of Spider-Man.
Three super-powered little girls constantly save the world (or at least the city of Townsville) from monsters, would-be conquerers and a few other gross things.
The further and darker adventures of Batman with a new Robin, a closer association with Batgirl and the previous Robin now as Nightwing.
A young boy who dreams of becoming a hero, stumbles across some cosmic stones of power. His dreams appear to have come true.
A scrawny 14-year-old, having discovered his inventor stepdad has three bionic, super-powered teens living cloistered in a secret lab beneath their home, brings them out into the world.

show_title: He-Man and the Masters of the Universe
synopsis: Eternia's Prince Adam discovers the power of Grayskull and transforms into He-Man, Master of the Universe. A reimagining of the classic animated series.
Federal agent Leon S. Kennedy teams up with TerraSave staff member Claire Redfield to investigate a zombie outbreak. Based on the popular video game series of the same name by Capcom.
The last son of the planet Krypton protects his adoptive home of Earth as the greatest of the superheroes.
A trio of reformed juvenile delinquents work as undercover cops.
Peter Parker, a new student at the famous Horizon High, fights evil super-villains as the costumed superhero, Spider-Man.
Five teenagers become the last line of defense for the galaxy in an intergalactic battle against the evil alien force led by King Zarkon.
In the future, long after the Batman has driven himself into exile, his legacy lives on in the form of the Birds of Prey--Black Canary, Oracle, and the Huntress.
The Powells are a typical American family living in Pacific Bay, California, whose members gain special powers after their plane crashes in the Amazon.

show_title: He-Man and the Masters of the Universe
synopsis: The most powerful man in the universe, He-Man, goes against the evil forces of Skeletor to save the planet Eternia and to protect the secrets of Castle Grayskull.
Two opposing factions of transforming alien robots engage in a battle that has the fate of Earth in the balance.
It centers around an egomaniacal supervillain with a really big head and a really little body, who struggles to maintain control of his evil organization and his demanding family.
A parody of reality shows cast with spoofs of several famous types of animated characters.
Satirical yet educational animated series about a young girl who is secretly the superhero Wordgirl, armed with superhuman strength, abilities, and a skilled vocabulary.

The adventures of Earth's martial arts defender Son Goku continue with a new family and the revelation of his alien origin. Now Goku and his allies must defend the planet from an onslaught of new extraterrestrial enemies.
Ben 10 is the fifth iteration of the Ben 10 franchise. It serves as a reboot of the television series loosely based upon the original series.

When young friends Connor, Amaya, and Greg put on their pajamas and activate their animal amulets, they turn into their alter egos: Catboy, Owlette, and Gekko as they embark on adventures that are filled with action.
With the powers given by the bite of a radioactive spider, a young man fights crime as a wall-crawling superhero.
A 14-year-old receives ghost powers and uses them to save the world.
After fully recovering from her nearly fatal bout of bionic rejection, Jaime Sommers, the first female cyborg, is assigned to spy missions of her own.

Dragon Ball tells the tale of a young warrior by the name of Son Goku, a young peculiar boy with a tail who embarks on a quest to become stronger and learns of the Dragon Balls, when, once all 7 are gathered, grant any wish of choice.
The adventures of a group of ten-year-old friends who fight for the right to do everything that adults restrict from them.
Gary Wallace and Wyatt Donnelly create their dream woman, Lisa, on their computer. Lisa has extraordinary powers and can grant the boys their wishes for short periods of time.
The misadventures of a boy genius and his annoying sister.
Johnny Bolt recruits a group of ragtag supervillains for one last heist. Their target: A ruthless super-powered crime boss. What can go wrong?
From the mind of comic book legend Stan Lee comes a bold new action crime series about a brilliant but flawed police officer with the power to control luck.
The further adventures of Buzz Lightyear as a Space Ranger of Star Command and his comrades.
Pamela Anderson provides the voice of Erotica Jones who is stripper by night and superhero Stripperella by even later at night.

One day, 14-year-old Yusuke Urameshi suddenly finds himself dead, having died pushing a child out of the way of oncoming traffic. Since he has such a bad personality, even the Spirit World ... See full summary »
The magical action-adventures of a teenage girl who learns of her destiny as the legendary warrior Sailor Moon and must band together with the other Sailor Scouts to defend the Earth and Galaxy.
After being betrayed and murdered by his employer, a government trained assassin is resurrected as a Hellspawn, then being forced to act as the reluctant leader of Hell's army.

Tarzan (Lord Greystoke), already well educated and fed up with civilization, returns to the jungle and, more or less assisted by chimpanzee Cheetah and orphan boy Jai, wages war against poachers and other bad guys.
After 74 villains break out of prison, Marvel's most powerful superheroes team up to capture all of them, and also to defend the Earth from widespread threats.
A group of schoolgirls discover they are incarnations of super-powered alien princesses, and use their abilities to defend the earth.
4 Teenage girls form Team RWBY and train to fight crime and monsters known as the Grimm, while the world of Remnant remains on the brink of an all out war.
The Winx have a mission in hand, reaching their final fairy stage. But trouble arises as Valtor escapes from the Omega Dimension and teams up with the Trix.
Teenage versions of DC Comics superheroines both attend high school and fight crime to protect the citizens of Metropolis.
A new team of superhuman power rangers must work together and use their new ninja powers to prevent evil from dominating the human race and from destroying the planet earth and the universe

Set in Manila where the mythical creatures of Philippine folklore live in hiding amongst humans, Alexandra Trese finds herself going head to head with a criminal underworld comprised of malevolent supernatural beings.
A young boy, able to transform into the superhero Captain Marvel, travels the country fighting evil and helping people.
